s -Carlo Paalambid farewell to his goal of repeating as an Olympic medalist.\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 271, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"score\": 0.6584459349881712, \"rank\": 0.3976026651834158, \"text\": \"Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9998934950656244, \"rank\": 0.00010553340825092363, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paalam saw his Paris Games campaign come to a screeching halt after a crushing split decision loss to Australia's Charlie Senior in the men's boxing 57kg quarterfinals at the North Paris Arena on Sunday, August 3.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 493, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.4888793250918571, \"rank\": 0.5803658047174227, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999672404561, \"rank\": 3.2759508507083056e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one of the most tightly contested fights of this Olympics, Senior earned the nod of three of the five judges by scores of 30-27, 29-28, 29-28, with the other two giving it 30-27, 29-28 to Paalam.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paalam, who wonsilverin the Tokyo Games three years ago, fell a wee bit short of a guaranteed medal as he lost the third round, 2-3.\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Senior repeatedly raised his hand to signal to the judges of his hits, although there were instances when he pulled off the move even when he missed.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bout could not have been any tighter after the first two rounds as Paalam and Senior each led in two scorecards, while the fifth judge counted it a tie going into the final salvo.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paalam is the third Filipino boxer to bow out of contention afterEumir Marcial(men's 80kg) andHergie Bacyadan(women's 75kg) dropped their opening bouts.\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The task of delivering the Philippines the elusive Olympic boxing gold now falls on the shoulders ofNesthy Petecio(women's 57kg) andAira Villegas(women's 50kg).\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9998934950656244, \"rank\": 0.00010553340825092363, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Petecio and Villegas are both a win away from the semifinals and a sure bronze.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\",